    <mj-section padding-top="30px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text mj-class="heading">THE WRIGHT TIME</mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="text">They say Red Bull gives you wings… I don’t know about that. Normally it gives me the shakes and a case of heartburn. What I do know is that on this day in 1903, the Wright brothers took some wings into the sky and flew the first “flying machine.” Being an Ohio boy, I appreciate the day that a couple of other Ohio boys changed the world. Fun fact though, the first flight only lasted 12 seconds. That’s it! However, those 12 seconds were enough to inspire them and to show that the impossible was indeed possible. Pretty cool, right? Just think, I’ve spent way more time than that just typing this intro and it’s way less impactful. Like in one-sixth of a minute they changed the way we travel and I’ve spent five minutes trying to think what GIF should go with this. Oh well, I guess it’s al-WRIGHT!</mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="text">Fridays left before Christmas: 1</mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="text">Let's go, folks!</mj-text>
        <mj-image src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/x7aLyUNtx12yPy0ASaD4SKku6Y0YREgpYdWByhdVh6Nj47N3CrsPL66b6u1Z101VrLhexvabrE0ziGE-DCJUZFFlSLtuiKgjvXP0pUeQgf0Mv7ZguC-sq2RzJqJOEXTjglz7IV6O" align="center" width="300px"></mj-image>
